Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:51.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.82,0:00:54.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,那是森林的守護者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.35,0:00:59.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,是為了守護森林  讓其存續的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:02.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,巡視森林
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.20,0:01:08.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,觀察植物  動物等一切生物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.01,0:01:11.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,不干涉食物鏈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.21,0:01:16.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,僅僅管理著自然之理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:22.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,森林是誕生生命  哺育生命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.38,0:01:26.73,somari text,,0,0,0,,並且是其最終回歸大地的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.16,0:01:29.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,森林有著其法則
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:35.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,我作為其法則的紐帶  在森林裡度過了千年的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.85,0:01:37.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,時機一到便回歸森林
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.89,0:01:43.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,我未曾懷疑過這是我的存在意義
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:46.12,somari text,,0,0,0,,直到那個時候為止…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:53.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:13.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,人類的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:19.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸…爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.23,0:02:28.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,她稱我為「父親」
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,----op----
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:42.83,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}何なんだろう　この胸のモヤモヤは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:42.83,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}心中的這份躁動  是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.13,0:02:50.59,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}洗いたてのタオルに顔を埋めるような
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.13,0:02:50.59,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}就像將臉埋入剛洗過的毛巾一般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.26,0:02:57.72,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}鳥が鳴いている　朝焼けのメロディー
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.26,0:02:57.72,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}鳥兒們吟唱著  朝霞的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:08.78,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}どこまで歩いても　この道は続いている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:08.78,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}無論走到哪  這道路都會延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:17.88,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}手を繋ぐよりも　指を繋ぐような
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:17.88,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}比起手牽手  更像是緊握這手指
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.02,0:03:24.65,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}寒い夜は寄り添い合って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.02,0:03:24.65,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}寒冷的夜晚彼此相依
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:30.01,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}星空の毛布で眠る
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:30.01,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}以星空為毯子安眠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:35.25,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}テーブルの向こうの笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:35.25,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}餐桌對面的笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:43.69,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}最果ての地を君と目指した
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:43.69,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}為你指向盡頭之地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:53.20,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}ありがとうはこっちの言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:53.20,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}我才該說謝謝你才對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:09.01,somari title,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,800)\blur5\pos(1618.8,1043.6)}旅行的父女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:14.52,somari text,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:15.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:30.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:32.37,somari text,,0,0,0,,給我站住  兔子！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:34.50,somari text - top,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.22,0:04:35.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,感謝你帶路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:37.29,somari text - top,,0,0,0,,喂  站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.84,0:04:38.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,你在這裡啊  索瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:40.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:47.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,我應該告訴過你不要擅自消失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:49.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,聽我說  雖然我讓蝴蝶逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:51.83,somari text,,0,0,0,,不過我發現了兔子就去追…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:54.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,在旅行中散開會有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:58.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要離開我目所能及的範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:02.32,somari text,,0,0,0,,那要看時間和場合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:07.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:14.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,城鎮  能看到城鎮了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:21.58,somari text,,0,0,0,,來啊  歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:24.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,之前真是多謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:25.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,不不  不用放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:28.64,somari text,,0,0,0,,你好  之前承您照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:30.98,somari text,,0,0,0,,走了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.42,0:05:35.59,somari text,,0,0,0,,這個城鎮好大啊  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:39.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,應該是至今為止拜訪的城鎮裡最繁榮的一個了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.41,0:05:41.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,與此相應的危險也會增加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,需要小心謹慎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:45.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,貓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:46.22,somari text,,0,0,0,,喂  貓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:47.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,come  on
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:48.52,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:52.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.02,0:05:54.52,somari text,,0,0,0,,我餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:05.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,吃飯！吃飯！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:07.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:09.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,今日的推薦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:11.70,somari text,,0,0,0,,燈籠魚包飯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:15.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,這是飽含必要營養的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:16.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要吃剩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:28.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:29.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:31.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸也嚐一口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:32.42,somari text,,0,0,0,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.96,0:06:36.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆只要有氧氣  陽光以及水就能活動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:38.80,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.41,0:06:41.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,客人您是哥雷姆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:42.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:45.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,這可真是少見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:46.12,somari text,,0,0,0,,我可是第一次見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:48.80,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆還真是嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:52.30,somari text,,0,0,0,,我還以為你們只待在森林裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:54.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,而且還帶著孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.95,0:06:56.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,那個孩子是什麼種族
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:06:59.23,somari text,,0,0,0,,屬於「牛角族」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.40,0:07:03.66,somari text,,0,0,0,,真的誒  長著一對可愛的角呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:06.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,話說回來  兩位旅客為什麼會來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.23,0:07:09.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,我們在找尋人類
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:10.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,人類？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:15.97,somari text,,0,0,0,,我們是為了找到人類  才踏上的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.94,0:07:20.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,不過你們有見到人類嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:25.67,somari text,,0,0,0,,說的也是  不久前市場上不就有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:29.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,人類嗎  那可真是很美味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:32.23,somari text,,0,0,0,,我還想再吃一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:36.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,不過為什麼人類消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:40.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,這是很久很久以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.16,0:07:47.47,somari text,,0,0,0,,我們和人類在彼此不知道的相隔甚遠的土地生存著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:53.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,就在這時  一位人類找到了我們的住所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:55.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,兩個種族相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.22,0:07:59.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,儘管相互震驚  不過接下來消除戒心後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:02.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,兩個種族就交流了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:09.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,不過  人類將我們稱之為異形  說著怪話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:12.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,為什麼你們長相都不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,有的長著很多眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.54,0:08:15.92,somari text,,0,0,0,,有的擁有蛇一樣的鱗片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:18.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,多麼噁心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:21.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,我們很是頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:24.22,somari text,,0,0,0,,為什麼人類這麼難相處
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.68,0:08:26.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,以貌取人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.58,0:08:29.58,somari text,,0,0,0,,明明很弱卻很固執  動不動就生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.14,0:08:33.47,somari text,,0,0,0,,最終這樣的聲音如波浪般散開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:35.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,我們與人類開始了戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:39.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,那是相當大的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:43.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,然後弱小的人類一瞬間就敗北
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:46.65,somari text,,0,0,0,,不知何時便消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.51,0:08:53.18,somari text,,0,0,0,,就這樣  我們迎來了沒有人類的和平世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.07,0:08:55.59,somari text,,0,0,0,,這是起源的故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:59.94,somari text,,0,0,0,,以前還流行過搜尋殘黨  狩獵人類呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.94,0:09:02.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯  當做寵物或者吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.94,0:09:05.04,somari text,,0,0,0,,不過怎麼說也不存在了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:07.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,現在住在這的就只有我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:13.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,哎呀  要回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:14.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:16.53,somari text,,0,0,0,,你們今晚住哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:18.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,野營
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:20.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎麼說這也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:23.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,還有小孩子在  很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.43,0:09:27.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,我會給你介紹旅館的  住在這個城鎮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.27,0:09:28.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,不  這就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:32.42,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  要住在這嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:33.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,住在這嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.48,0:09:38.98,somari text,,0,0,0,,住在這！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:43.30,somari text,,0,0,0,,被窩軟綿綿的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:48.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,雖然沒有在這停留的預定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:50.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.69,0:09:57.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.02,0:09:58.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,探險
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:01.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,難以理解的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:04.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,那個  我和爸爸留宿很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.11,0:10:06.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:07.27,somari text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:09.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸不開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:11.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆沒有感情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:14.88,somari text,,0,0,0,,不開心的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:19.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,這樣接著旅行會很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:21.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,能修好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:23.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:24.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:28.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸能修好  爸爸能修好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:29.94,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.74,0:10:32.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:34.94,somari text,,0,0,0,,安靜點  別動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:57.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,只是個客人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:03.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸慌了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:06.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,我無法理解你因何愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:09.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,而且  我剛才也說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:11.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,說到底哥雷姆沒有感情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:14.02,somari text,,0,0,0,,可是爸爸的身體都僵硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.63,0:11:16.73,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗都看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:20.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,你的發言是錯誤的見解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:22.95,somari text,,0,0,0,,你絕對慌了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:26.12,somari text,,0,0,0,,明天要早起  到就寢的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:27.61,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要  我還不想睡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:28.47,somari text,,0,0,0,,否決
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:30.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,否決你的否決
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:12:00.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,哇  角修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:02.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:04.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,別一直摸它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:06.07,somari text,,0,0,0,,有可能會又壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:08.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,謝謝爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.84,0:12:09.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,不用感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:13.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,今天去哪兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:15.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,補充消耗品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:17.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,買東西呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:53.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.77,0:14:11.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,太廉價了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:14.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,之前的城鎮出了兩倍的價錢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:19.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,不過老闆  這石頭在這邊兒可不是太稀有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:22.17,somari text,,0,0,0,,這點我覺得就合適了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:23.59,somari text,,0,0,0,,難以接受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:26.04,somari text,,0,0,0,,我希望給一個合適的價錢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:30.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,就算你這麼說  這石頭也就是這個樣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:32.12,somari text,,0,0,0,,貓？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:35.31,somari text,,0,0,0,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:39.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,客人  這可是很貴重的寶石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.01,somari text,,0,0,0,,眼睛  還是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:45.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,硅酸鹽為主要成分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:47.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,非晶狀物質
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:51.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,根據我的解析  這是贗品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.40,0:14:53.61,somari text,,0,0,0,,你哪來的依據
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:58.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆的眼睛能夠看穿世間萬物的構成物質
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:02.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,陳列的裝飾品的金屬部分不是純金
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:06.18,somari text,,0,0,0,,而是含有78%的劣質銅製品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.76,0:15:08.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,2%是金色的染色劑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:11.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,大多的寶石都是玻璃珠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:13.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,剩下的都是劣質品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:18.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,也就是說  這家店的商品八成都是假貨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:23.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,店主  你能推測出我的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:34.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.44,0:15:38.06,somari text,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:40.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,拿了就趕緊滾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:42.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,不必多言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:44.18,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗  走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:51.26,somari text,,0,0,0,,又來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:22.27,somari text,,0,0,0,,喂  小貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:24.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,你在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:36.06,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:39.07,somari text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.57,0:17:41.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,我在這
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.24,0:17:44.06,somari text,,0,0,0,,小貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:46.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,沒事吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:49.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,不是小貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:52.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,覺得麻煩  本來是不想理你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:55.42,somari text,,0,0,0,,但你一直跟著我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:59.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,要是因為我迷路了  我也睡不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.34,0:18:03.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,才沒有迷路  只是在亂逛而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:06.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以說你這叫迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:08.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:12.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,那些別管了  讓我摸摸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:14.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,說了不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:18.65,somari text,,0,0,0,,真是的  你是哪來的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:20.66,somari text,,0,0,0,,一個人跑到這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:27.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,感覺你身上有一股熟悉的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.84,0:18:30.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎麼形容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:32.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:35.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,十分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:38.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,美味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:48.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:51.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,趕緊從這裡離開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:00.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:02.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:03.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:07.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,果然爸爸你會來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:12.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,回旅館了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.35,0:19:13.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:18.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:22.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,我說  剛才見著了那個帶著小孩的哥雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.08,0:19:24.10,somari text,,0,0,0,,超級可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:26.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,你肯定幹了什麼壞事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:27.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:31.23,somari text,,0,0,0,,只是感覺那個小孩特別美味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:33.32,somari text,,0,0,0,,說了出來  他突然就
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:37.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,你居然連這麼小的小孩兒都不放過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:39.50,somari text,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:40.70,somari text,,0,0,0,,真差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:43.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,說了不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:51.10,somari text,,0,0,0,,剛才還好趕到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:54.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,要是被感知到是人類就危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:19:57.80,somari text,,0,0,0,,小孩子這種生物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:00.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,在好奇感興趣的事物面前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.04,0:20:03.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,有著無法乖乖地待著的傾向
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:04.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:06.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:09.32,somari text,,0,0,0,,剛才是怎麼知道索瑪麗在哪兒的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:11.82,somari text,,0,0,0,,觀察了你的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:13.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,觀察？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:16.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,每當索瑪麗從我的身旁離開時
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:20.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,都是被什麼東西所吸引了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.00,0:20:23.57,somari text,,0,0,0,,這種情感無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:26.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是觀察和分析卻是可行的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.50,0:20:29.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,因為是第一次與人類小孩接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.13,0:20:32.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,需要多花一些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.14,0:20:37.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是  之後的旅程要是再迷路了可是大問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:41.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,以後禁止隨便從我的身邊離開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.73,0:20:43.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,這個得視場合和時間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:46.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:50.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:54.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,觀察了城鎮的居民後發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:57.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,牽手這種行為
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.45,0:20:59.57,somari text,,0,0,0,,防止單獨行動是很有效的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.43,0:21:02.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.99,0:21:03.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:08.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:10.49,somari text,,0,0,0,,一隻手握住就行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:12.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:15.04,somari text,,0,0,0,,這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:16.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.25,0:21:22.65,somari text,,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.94,0:21:28.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  有蝶蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.07,0:21:30.55,somari text,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.46,0:21:34.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,確實是一種防止單獨行動有效的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:38.97,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是也極大的限制了彼此的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:43.37,somari text,,0,0,0,,有必要研究出一種更高效率的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.99,0:21:45.49,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.86,0:21:48.18,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗覺得這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,0:21:51.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:23.09,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}並ぶ影の大きさ比べ笑う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:23.09,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}比較著並排的影子相視而笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.47,0:22:26.66,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}夕暮れを背に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.47,0:22:26.66,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}把夕陽甩在身後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:37.73,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}そっと風に乗せたのは　まだ小さな願い事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:37.73,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}乘風而去的是那小小的祈願
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:44.76,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}永遠とか　生命だとか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:44.76,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}什麼是永遠  什麼是生命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:49.36,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}何も分からずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:49.36,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}我還一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.83,0:23:01.64,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}真っ直ぐな瞳で　見上げた横顔は眩しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.83,0:23:01.64,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}只知道當我抬頭仰望你時  你的側臉總是那麼地閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:07.99,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}重ねた手に伝う温もりは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:07.99,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}手牽著手傳遞的這份溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.49,0:23:12.51,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}どんなときも愛をくれたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.49,0:23:12.51,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}無論何時都在給予我愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.89,0:23:18.40,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}溢れ出すこの想いが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.89,0:23:18.40,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}這不斷溢出的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.73,0:23:24.17,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}あなたに届く日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.73,0:23:24.17,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}直到傳達到給你的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.57,0:23:32.72,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}交わした約束進もう  未来へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.57,0:23:32.72,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}向著共同許下的諾言和未來  前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:41.02,somari title,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,0)\blur6\pos(1588.8,1062)}野草與鬼的住處
